s0 ws0">随地帮助可怜的众生。 </div><div class="t m0 x1b h4 y1dd ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls4d ws0">在座各位扪心自问：<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="ls2a">“我有没有大乘的善心？”恐怕不</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y1de ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls28 ws0">一定有。看见可怜众生时，你<span class="ls10">不但不帮助，也许会想：<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="ls2d">“可</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y58 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">怜之人必有可恨之处，他活该受罪……”如果是这种心态，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y59 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">跟大乘的发心就相去甚远了。</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
